Flowcounter README

Goal: This module counts number of incoming flow records.

Input Interface: UniRec format specified by template from -u parameter.
Output Interface: none or @VOLUME record, affected by -o parameter.

Parameters: -u TMPL 	Specify UniRec template expected on the input interface.
	    -p N	Show progress bar - print a dot every N flows. 
	    -P CHAR	When -p parameter is enabled, print CHAR instead of dot.
	    -o SEC	Send @VOLUME record filled with current counters every
			SEC second(s). Interval for SEC is (0;1000).
